<plot>A feature documentary about satirical rock star Manuel João Vieira who ran as a candidate for the Presidency of Portugal in 2001. Altough he didn't collect the number of signatures needed to officially put him on the ballots, Vieira's surreal campaign appearances on television talk shows, radio and concerts took the country by storm and left everybody laughing. A political, comedic and musical documentary!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?404025</url></doc>
